# Local-fs storage adapter scratch — uploaded documents in dev only.
# Production storage is a remote adapter (S3/etc); these files exist only when
# PROVIDER_STORAGE=local on a developer machine and should never be committed.
# Double-glob so a stray .uploads/ anywhere in the tree (e.g. from a relative-
# path bug in an earlier adapter version) is still ignored.
**/.uploads/
/tmp/shipops-storage-smoke/

